<plot>Nearly every major element of making the film Thelma &amp; Louise (1991) is examined here from how the script was written to how Ridley Scott got involved, to how the big tanker explosion was pulled off. Some funny stories are shared and some great trivia as to what was improvised on set and actually left in the film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?603373</url></doc>
